methods.getShort:
Get a single short from this region.

*Overload 1*  
  :param elementIndex: (long) - Element (short) rowSet in the table's address space
  :return: (short) The short value at the specified element (short) rowSet
  
*Overload 2*  
  :param context: (io.deephaven.engine.chunk.ChunkSource.FillContext) - A RegionContextHolder to enable resource caching where suitable, with current
                       region rowSet pointing to this region
  :param elementIndex: (long) - Element (short) rowSet in the table's address space
  :return: (short) The short value at the specified element (short) rowSet
